# Never add a stray `tree-sitter-*.json` file here except `tree-sitter.json`:
# the CLI treats matching names as grammar roots and looks for `<name>/tree-sitter.json`,
# which triggers "Not a directory" if the path is a file (e.g. old `tree-sitter-ci-config.json`).
tree-sitter-ci-config.json
